OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784623688
OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to man who died
OL,4,Cnear the Royal Welsh Show
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a "dear and
OL,7,Fbeloved" man who died at a campsite
OL,8,Fnear the Royal Welsh showground.
OL,10,FThe man has been named as 25-year-old
OL,11,FDewi Evans of Llanfihangel Glyn Myfyr,
OL,12,FCorwen.
OL,14,FPolice were called to an emergency
OL,15,Fmedical incident on Saturday night
OL,16,F(July 18) at Penmaenau Farm caravan
OL,17,Fpark - the biggest campsite used by
OL,18,FRoyal Welsh visitors each year, with
OL,19,Fthousands of people on site.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
