PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784623688
OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to man who died
OL,4,Cnear the Royal Welsh Show
OL,6,FPaying tribute, his family said: "Dewi
OL,7,FAeron Evans, a beloved and dear son,
OL,8,Fbrother and grandson; will be a huge
OL,9,Floss to the family and community in
OL,10,FUwchaled. The family and community
OL,11,Fwould appreciate privacy at this
OL,12,Fdifficult time."
OL,14,FEmergency services had been called at
OL,15,F10.30pm on Saturday but despite
OL,16,Fparamedics efforts, the 25-year old
OL,17,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,19,FThree men have been arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of drug offences in
OL,21,Fconnection with this incident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
