PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784623688
OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to man who died
OL,4,Cnear the Royal Welsh Show
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Steve Davies
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a tragic incident, and
OL,8,Four thoughts remain with the young
OL,9,Fman's family at this difficult time.
OL,11,F"I would like to reassure the public
OL,12,Fthat this is an isolated incident, and
OL,13,Fthe death is currently being treated
OL,14,Fas unexplained.
OL,16,F"There is no evidence of any ongoing
OL,17,Frisk to the wider public in connection
OL,18,Fwith this sad incident."
